name: Edooni Solutions
overview:
Edooni Solutions Private Limited is a provider of e-learning platform consisting of innovative applications which run online. It provides solutions to students preparing for entrance exams in MBA, Engineering,Medical, GATE and IAS domains.

Its end-to-end solution spanning question insertion , test creation, test taking and test assessment is one of the most robust in the market and it is being used by entities like McGraw-Hill - Mindworkzz (www.mindworkzz.com) , Bansal Classes (www.bansaltestprep.com) etc.
